Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.05,IN_S_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,卻為相互疏遠而吐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:54.35,IN_S_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,傷人利刃皆由口出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.37,IN_K_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,但又何妨不移堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:59.61,IN_K_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,過去點滴散落於心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.75,0:18:04.18,IN_K_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,羈絆皆為你我維繫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.75,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}攜手織就　萬千奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.49,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}此刻化作　莫敵之力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.13,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}向著明天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:13.19,IN_H_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,引吭高歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.55,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}向著世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.92,0:18:20.69,IN_N_CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFF0065&}晶淚隨之飄卻
