Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統運轉正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距網絡干擾生效還剩300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經失去了能夠解釋一切的時間和言語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請原諒我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲尼
